{
  "stem": "1479.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the beginning work-- working in the quarry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was working late on building the roads, the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we were working in a barrack making necklaces for the Nazi soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were sending out these on the [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tour ?] [? de ?] France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The last job in Plaszow for me was in the laundry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was on the night shift.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "According to all what we know, that Amon Goeth passed by the barrack, and he noticed that we were not working too hard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The following morning, our work in the laundry was dissolved.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were working over there again for a few days by building the roads.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At that time, this was already March 13, 1943 when the Krakow ghetto was liquidating.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is a date for me is gonna live forever because during the liquidation of Krakow ghetto, my parents-- both parents-- were murdered during the liquidation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And other members of the family, but mainly my parents were murdered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were buried, which during the liquidation, there were thousands of people killed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the bodies were brought to Plaszow and buried in a mass grave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A few days later after the liquidation of Krakow ghetto, they rounded up a group of women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Since this was 1943-- it started in '42-- there were daily selections and daily deportations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "When they rounded us up, we were almost certain that we would be sent away from Plaszow somewheres to a death camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Little did we know that we were the lucky people because other groups, exactly what had happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were rounded up, put on the-- into the cattle cars, and they were sent away to the death camps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I believe in miracles because this was like a miracle.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
